snippet.title: Linxy The Lynx - Steam Next Fest: October 2023 Demo
snippet.description:
Linxy is known for saving his home (Mangoberry Island) from the nefarious Prof.B.Ray on a weekly basis and this time it's not all that different, B.Ray is up to some scheme that revolves using his Nature Taker-er to power his Linxy Destroyer-er! Explore many time periods as you journey Across Time to continue your pursuit to stop the evil professor and then well... where else will your journey take you?

Linxy The Lynx (C) CrazyLegends Studios Ltd.
Release Date: 2024
